This is the first of 9 entries in The Cheesiest Travel Photo Contest that I’ll be posting through Wednesday. Check out entry #1, entry #2, entry#3, entry #4, and entry #5 and vote for your favorites beginning next Monday, August 24th.

“While walking by a local Chinese tourist dressed up in a costume, I was coerced into being a prop in his photo shoot”

One random subscriber will be picked and given a prize also. The easiest way to enter is to sign up for daily email updates below or follow me on Twitter.
